('acount', '<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); clear: left; font-family: arial; line-height: 16px; text-align: justify; ">\r\n	<span style="color:#0000cd;"><em><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;"><strong>1. L&agrave;m sao tạo t&agrave;i khoản tr&ecirc;n DealXinh.com</strong></span></span></em></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); clear: left; font-family: arial; line-height: 16px; text-align: justify; ">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); clear: left; font-family: arial; line-height: 16px; text-align: justify; ">\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;">Chọn &quot;Đăng k&yacute;&quot; trong giao di&ecirc;̣n b&acirc;́t k&igrave; của DealXinh.com</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); clear: left; font-family: arial; line-height: 16px; text-align: justify; ">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); clear: left; font-family: arial; line-height: 16px; text-align: center; ">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 12px; "><span style="font-family: tahoma, geneva, sans-serif; "><img alt="" src="http://cheapdeal.vn/Uploads/images/dkdn(1).gif" style="border: 0px; " /></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); clear: left; font-family: arial; line-height: 16px; text-align: justify; ">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); clear: left; font-family: arial; line-height: 16px; text-align: justify; ">\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;">Sau đ&oacute; ho&agrave;n t&acirc;́t c&aacute;c th&ocirc;ng tin c&acirc;̀n thi&ecirc;́t cho vi&ecirc;̣c l&acirc;̣p t&agrave;i khoản</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); clear: left; font-family: arial; line-height: 16px; text-align: justify; ">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); clear: left; font-family: arial; line-height: 16px; text-align: center; ">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 12px; "><span style="font-family: tahoma, geneva, sans-serif; "><img alt="" src="http://cheapdeal.vn/Uploads/images/dkodn.gif" style="border: 0px; width: 500px; height: 628px; " /></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); clear: left; font-family: arial; line-height: 16px; text-align: justify; ">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); clear: left; font-family: arial; line-height: 16px; text-align: justify; ">\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;">N&ecirc;́u bạn l&agrave; th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n của DealXinh.com, bạn chỉ c&acirc;̀n cung c&acirc;́p địa chỉ mail v&agrave; m&acirc;̣t kh&acirc;̉u m&agrave; bạn đ&atilde; d&ugrave;ng đăng k&yacute;</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); clear: left; font-family: arial; line-height: 16px; text-align: justify; ">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); clear: left; font-family: arial; line-height: 16px; text-align: center; ">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 12px; "><span style="font-family: tahoma, geneva, sans-serif; "><img alt="" src="http://cheapdeal.vn/Uploads/images/dn.gif" style="border: 0px; width: 500px; height: 323px; " /></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); clear: left; font-family: arial; line-height: 16px; text-align: justify; ">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); clear: left; font-family: arial; line-height: 16px; text-align: justify; ">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); clear: left; font-family: arial; line-height: 16px; text-align: justify; ">\r\n	<span style="color:#0000cd;"><em><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;"><strong>2. L&agrave;m sao để kiểm tra t&igrave;nh trạng đơn h&agrave;ng?</strong></span></span></em></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); clear: left; font-family: arial; line-height: 16px; text-align: justify; ">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); clear: left; font-family: arial; line-height: 16px; text-align: justify; ">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;"><span style="color:#000000;">Bạn cần phải đăng nhập để xem c&aacute;c đơn h&agrave;ng đ&atilde; đặt.</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); clear: left; font-family: arial; line-height: 16px; text-align: justify; ">\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;">Bạn cũng c&oacute; th&ecirc;̉ thay đ&ocirc;̉i th&ocirc;ng tin c&aacute;c nh&acirc;n trong mục &quot;T&agrave;i khoản của t&ocirc;i&quot;</span></span></span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); clear: left; font-family: arial; line-height: 16px; text-align: center; ">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 12px; "><span style="font-family: tahoma, geneva, sans-serif; "><img alt="" src="http://cheapdeal.vn/Uploads/images/taikhoancuatoi.gif" style="border: 0px; width: 306px; height: 151px; " /></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); clear: left; font-family: arial; line-height: 16px; text-align: justify; ">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); clear: left; font-family: arial; line-height: 16px; text-align: justify; ">\r\n	<span style="color:#0000cd;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;"><strong><em>3. L&agrave;m th&ecirc;́ n&agrave;o đ&ecirc;̉ quản l&yacute; đơn h&agrave;ng ?</em></strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); clear: left; font-family: arial; line-height: 16px; text-align: justify; ">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); clear: left; font-family: arial; line-height: 16px; text-align: justify; ">\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;">Vi&ecirc;̣c thay đ&ocirc;̉i đơn h&agrave;ng được di&ecirc;̃n ra sau khi bạn đăng nh&acirc;̣p, th&ocirc;ng tin v&ecirc;̀ c&aacute;c đơn h&agrave;ng trong qu&aacute; khứ sẽ được li&ecirc;̣t k&ecirc;&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); clear: left; font-family: arial; line-height: 16px; text-align: justify; ">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); clear: left; font-family: arial; line-height: 16px; text-align: center; ">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 12px; "><span style="font-family: tahoma, geneva, sans-serif; "><img alt="" src="http://cheapdeal.vn/Uploads/images/lichsudonhang.gif" style="border: 0px; width: 500px; height: 130px; " /></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); clear: left; font-family: arial; line-height: 16px; text-align: justify; ">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); clear: left; font-family: arial; line-height: 16px; text-align: justify; ">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); clear: left; font-family: arial; line-height: 16px; text-align: justify; ">\r\n	<span style="color:#0000cd;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;"><strong><em>4. L&agrave;m sao để đăng k&yacute; nhận th&ocirc;ng tin khuyến mại</em></strong></span></span></span><span style="color:#000000;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;"><strong>?</strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); clear: left; font-family: arial; line-height: 16px; text-align: justify; ">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); clear: left; font-family: arial; line-height: 16px; text-align: justify; ">\r\n	<span style="color:#000000;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;">Bạn c&oacute; thể v&agrave;o mục quản l&yacute; t&agrave;i khoản để đăng k&yacute; nhận email từ những th&agrave;nh phố m&agrave; bạn quan t&acirc;m. Lưu &yacute;: Khi bạn chọn đăng k&iacute; nh&acirc;̣n email đồng nghĩa với vi&ecirc;̣c bạn l&agrave; m&ocirc;̣t kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng của&nbsp;</span></span></span><strong style="font-family: ''times new roman'', times, serif; font-size: 16px;">Dealxinh.com</strong><span style="color:#000000;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;">, do đ&oacute;, th&ocirc;ng tin của bạn sẽ được d&ugrave;ng đ&ecirc;̉ phục vụ c&ocirc;ng t&aacute;c Chăm s&oacute;c kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng.</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); clear: left; font-family: arial; line-height: 16p